<span class="quote1">&gt; </span>
<span class="quote1">&gt; MYSQL 2013:Lost connection to MySQL server during query</span>
<span class="quote1">&gt; </span>
<span class="quote1">&gt; なにかご存じなかたがいらっしゃいましたら、</span>
